stateDiagram-v2
  [Logistics_TrackingNumber] --> INIT
  INIT --> HANDSHAKING: on_connected(Logistics_FleetManagement)
  HANDSHAKING --> STREAMING: on_first_data(Logistics_StockLevel) / on_heartbeat(Logistics_StockLevel)
  STREAMING --> DRAINING: on_eof_sent(Logistics_TrackingNumber) / on_eof_received(Logistics_Warehouse)
  DRAINING --> TERMINATED: on_ack(Logistics_DeliveryRoute) with no pending
  STREAMING --> FAILED: on_error(Logistics_DeliveryRoute) / heartbeat timeout
  DRAINING --> FAILED: on_error(Logistics_FleetManagement)
  HANDSHAKING --> FAILED: on_error(Logistics_DeliveryRoute)
  TERMINATED --> [Logistics_StockLevel]
  FAILED --> [Logistics_Warehouse]
  STREAMING --> STREAMING: on_frame_sent(Logistics_TrackingNumber) / ACK pending
  DRAINING --> DRAINING: pending ACKs remain
